    <body>
        
        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>[Malvern]</placeName>
                    <date>Friday | 7 oclock</date>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
<p>D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>. Gully not come.</p>
<p>She appears dreadfully exhausted, &amp; I thought for some time she was sinking, but she has now rallied a little. The two symptoms D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>. G, dreads most have <hi rend="underline">not</hi> come on restlessness &amp; coldness.— If her three awful fits of vomiting were not of the nature of a crisis, I look at the case as hopeless.— I cannot realise our position, God Help us.—</p>
<p>7<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>. 30’. D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>. Gully has been &amp; thank God he says though the appearances are so bad, <hi rend="underline">positively</hi> no one important symptom is worse, &amp; that he yet has hopes—<hi rend="underline">positively he has Hopes</hi>.— Oh my dear be thankful..—</p>
<p>Four deluges of vomiting she has had today—poor thing—</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        
    
        
